  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  CT/MRI diagnosed stage cT1-4N0-3;

          -  Histologically confirmed anal squamous carcinoma;

          -  KPS &gt;= 70

          -  Adequate organ function;

          -  No previous radiotherapy or chemotherapy;

          -  No surgery.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Previous malignant cancer history;

          -  Allegic to 5-fu or MMC
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
